= Test Simple

```{r setup}
#| echo: false
x <- 42
name <- "Alice"
```

Test inline display: The value is #r[x] and the name is #r[name].

```{r calc}
y <- x * 2
print(y)
```

Test with side-effect verb:

#r:run[
  result_label <- "Final result"
  multiplier <- 3
]

The #r[result_label] is #r[x * multiplier].
